sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant InlineP as Ragas Inline Provider<br/>in-process
    participant RemoteP as Ragas Remote Provider<br/>in-process
    participant InferAPI as Inference API<br/>in-process
    participant DataIO as DatasetIO API<br/>in-process
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPPod1 as KFP Pod: retrieve_data<br/>ephemeral
    participant KFPPod2 as KFP Pod: run_ragas<br/>ephemeral
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,DataIO: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation (in-process)
        Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
        LLS->>InlineP: Delegate eval request
        InlineP->>DataIO: iterrows() — fetch dataset<br/>in-process call
        DataIO-->>InlineP: Dataset rows
        InlineP->>InferAPI: LLM completions via LlamaStackInlineLLM<br/>in-process (max_workers=1)
        InferAPI-->>InlineP: LLM responses
        InlineP->>InferAPI: Embeddings via LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings<br/>in-process (max_workers=1)
        InferAPI-->>InlineP: Embedding vectors
        Note over InlineP: Ragas evaluate() via<br/>asyncio.to_thread()
        InlineP-->>LLS: Evaluation results
        LLS-->>Client: JSON response<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)
        Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
        LLS->>RemoteP: Delegate eval request
        RemoteP->>KFP: create_run_from_pipeline_func<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OAuth)
        KFP-->>RemoteP: Run ID
        RemoteP-->>LLS: Job submitted (run_id)
        LLS-->>Client: Job ID response

        Note over KFP,S3: Async pipeline execution
        KFP->>KFPPod1: Schedule retrieve_data
        KFPPod1->>LLS: GET datasets & rows<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
        LLS-->>KFPPod1: Dataset content
        KFPPod1->>KFPPod2: Pass data artifact

        KFPPod2->>LLS: LLM inference calls<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
        LLS-->>KFPPod2: Inference results
        Note over KFPPod2: Run Ragas evaluation
        KFPPod2->>S3: PUT results.jsonl<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials

        Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job-status<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
        LLS->>RemoteP: Check status
        RemoteP->>KFP: Get run status<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        KFP-->>RemoteP: SUCCEEDED
        RemoteP-->>LLS: Status: completed

        Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job-result<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
        LLS->>RemoteP: Get results
        RemoteP->>S3: GET results.jsonl<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: AWS IAM (via s3fs/pandas)
        S3-->>RemoteP: JSONL data
        RemoteP-->>LLS: Parsed evaluation results
        LLS-->>Client: JSON response
    end
